I read through some of the posts on the EZ Board where Nightowl posted his adventure and read though this one. A few things I wish to point out. One, Why is it imposible to build a Ram while hidden. Find a nice little hole and build it. Bigger things have been hidden and walked out. Like oh....TV sets! Yes, this happens regulary in RL. Security becomes lax and things that should be obvious are over looked. I know, I know, But a Ram? Well look at it this way. If a Border Guard or what ever can see a Stealthed Assassin running across the feild at 1000 yards or waht ever and take off after him, why not let them get SOME benift from a skill we dump a ton of points into. I do belive that the Guards should be nerfed. The fact that they can AUTOMATICLY see right through stealth is just out right wrong. Highly Trained or not, there still should be SOME chance for them to go unnoticed right under their noses.<br>
<br>
As far as this takeing away from the game? PLEASE, for once one of us stealthers we able to do something other then get 20 tanks and 10 healers/casters to play Divertion while we sneak behind and get a Caster or two befor we are ganked. My personal opinion, I would love to see this happen alot more and yes, even to my own Relic keeps. That just tells me that I can one day sneak in, grab some pricy crap and bolt out the door, return home and be welcomed as a Hero! Plus have all the Ladys soon at my exspertise. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :smokin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smokin.gif ALT=":smokin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
